PizzaFLIX Presents Classic Movie Monday
Stars: Marian Marsh, Joan Marsh, Kenneth Thomson
Directed by: Christy Cabanne

A cynical city girl seeks to protect her innocent younger sibling from the evils of men... but little sis has her own ideas.

TRIVIA: Marian & Joan Marsh play sisters in this film, but not in real life.

metadata.Plot: A savvy city girl tries to protect her naive sister, who has just moved from the country, from the temptations--and men--of big-city life.
metadata.Writer: Sam Mintz, Barry Barringer, F. Hugh Herbert
metadata.Actors: Marian Marsh, Kenneth Thomson, Joan Marsh
